          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Preventing Civilian Casualties in Military Operations Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to report annually to the congressional defense committees on civilian casualties caused as a result of U. S. military operations during the preceding year.</p>]]></text>
